1
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:12,000
You guys...

2
00:01:16,879 --> 00:01:18,079
What's going on here?

3
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:22,760
Get out here.

4
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,200
Honey.

5
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:31,680
Let's go home.

6
00:01:31,799 --> 00:01:32,879
Why did you drink so much?

7
00:01:34,719 --> 00:01:35,319
President Su.

8
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:36,599
Thanks for looking after my husband.

9
00:01:37,879 --> 00:01:38,560
Oh, not at all.

10
00:01:39,040 --> 00:01:39,719
He had too much to drink.

11
00:01:39,879 --> 00:01:40,760
Just looking for a place to throw up.

12
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:42,480
Sorry to bother you.

13
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:47,560
Honey.

14
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,480
Love you.

15
00:02:02,079 --> 00:02:02,760
Bro.

16
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:03,920
Are you really drunk?

17
00:02:04,519 --> 00:02:05,480
What do you think?

18
00:02:06,439 --> 00:02:08,159
Do you think I get drunk that easily?

19
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:10,960
Just a bit dizzy and nauseous.

20
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,080
Oh, give me a break.

21
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:14,080
Your tongue is all tied up.

22
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,000
And you're not drunk?

23
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:17,199
What really happened tonight?

24
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,759
I was having fun tonight.

25
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:22,639
Had a few extra drinks.

26
00:02:24,599 --> 00:02:25,680
But that Han Lin,

27
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:27,599
he kept pushing drinks on me.

28
00:02:27,879 --> 00:02:28,879
Stop bringing up Han Lin.

29
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,360
In the elevator,

30
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:32,159
I only saw you and Su Yuanyuan.

31
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:33,520
Listen here, Xiao,

32
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:34,719
have you had enough of the good life?

33
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,280
If so, we can get a divorce anytime.

34
00:02:36,879 --> 00:02:37,639
At the hotel,

35
00:02:37,879 --> 00:02:38,919
I gave you plenty of respect.

36
00:02:39,319 --> 00:02:40,280
But don't push it too far.

37
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:42,960
Honey.

38
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:45,439
I haven't done

39
00:02:45,439 --> 00:02:46,360
a single thing to wrong you.

40
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:48,840
If you don't believe me...

41
00:02:49,479 --> 00:02:50,080
If you don't...

42
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,280
Go check for yourself.

43
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,080
Honey, what are you doing?

44
00:02:55,879 --> 00:02:57,520
Su Yuanyuan's pined for you for years.

45
00:02:57,759 --> 00:02:59,000
Don't you want to settle it?

46
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:00,439
Or...

47
00:03:01,599 --> 00:03:02,240
I could consider

48
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:02,960
stepping aside for her.

49
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:04,240
Honey.

50
00:03:05,159 --> 00:03:05,840
Am I really

51
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:06,840
so worthless to you?

52
00:03:07,719 --> 00:03:08,439
Anyone who wants me

53
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:09,759
can just take me, is that it?

54
00:03:10,599 --> 00:03:11,319
Alright, alright.

55
00:03:11,639 --> 00:03:12,680
I'm sure she's just joking.

56
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,960
I, He Junjie, swear on my honor,

57
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:16,639
my bro has never had

58
00:03:16,719 --> 00:03:18,039
the slightest interest in Su Yuanyuan.

59
00:03:18,199 --> 00:03:19,759
Never has, never will.

60
00:03:20,599 --> 00:03:21,479
You two brothers

61
00:03:21,479 --> 00:03:22,639
are thick as thieves.

62
00:03:22,919 --> 00:03:23,759
As if I'd believe you.

63
00:03:25,639 --> 00:03:26,439
Honey.

64
00:03:27,319 --> 00:03:27,960
Don't be mad.

65
00:03:28,759 --> 00:03:29,319
Su Yuanyuan and I

66
00:03:29,319 --> 00:03:30,280
have absolutely nothing going on.

67
00:03:31,199 --> 00:03:32,199
She deliberately got me drunk.

68
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:34,000
Honey.

69
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,199
Only you

70
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:38,639
are the brightest star in my night sky.

71
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,280
Sweet talker.

72
00:03:42,879 --> 00:03:43,719
I'll deal with you when we get home.

73
00:03:44,719 --> 00:03:46,879
You two look like you're fighting,

74
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:48,879
but really you're just flaunting your love.

75
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:55,400
I ran into Li Yao the other day.

76
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:56,400
I hear

77
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:58,159
he's running a construction crew now.

78
00:03:59,639 --> 00:04:01,560
After Li Yao got fired seven years ago,

79
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:02,919
he moved to another city.

80
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,639
Now he's back doing construction.

81
00:04:05,159 --> 00:04:05,879
Could it be

82
00:04:05,919 --> 00:04:07,080
that Han Lin got him the job?

83
00:04:08,039 --> 00:04:08,639
Li Yao.

84
00:04:10,319 --> 00:04:10,960
Han Lin.

85
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:13,919
Su Yuanyuan.

86
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:37,519
President Su.

87
00:04:38,199 --> 00:04:38,800
Come on.

88
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:42,519
Oh my.

89
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:45,720
So how was it?

90
00:04:45,879 --> 00:04:46,920
Your wedding night.

91
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:47,959
How did the battle go?

92
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,040
What nonsense are you spouting?

93
00:04:50,439 --> 00:04:51,720
After you left last night,

94
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,560
He Junjie brought

95
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,319
Yang Hui and the others over.

96
00:04:53,639 --> 00:04:54,600
You didn't even give me a heads-up.

97
00:04:55,759 --> 00:04:56,879
I honestly had no idea.

98
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:58,600
President Su.

99
00:04:58,800 --> 00:04:59,720
Calm down first.

100
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:01,079
By the way,

101
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,160
once the contract is signed later,

102
00:05:03,279 --> 00:05:04,720
can I get my commission first?

103
00:05:06,199 --> 00:05:06,920
Without you,

104
00:05:07,279 --> 00:05:08,160
I could still secure

105
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,040
the marketing agency rights

106
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:09,879
for Wanhe Mansion Phase Two.

107
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:13,240
Now, don't say it like that.

108
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,240
All these years, what I've done for you...

109
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,480
What's the rush?

110
00:05:16,319 --> 00:05:17,680
It hasn't been signed yet, has it?

111
00:05:19,959 --> 00:05:20,800
It's settled, then.

112
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,639
For Wanhe Mansion Phase Two,

113
00:05:31,639 --> 00:05:32,439
the marketing agency rights,

114
00:05:32,519 --> 00:05:33,959
you've already shortlisted three firms.

115
00:05:35,759 --> 00:05:37,160
Which one are you planning to sign?

116
00:05:37,639 --> 00:05:38,160
Chairman Zheng.

117
00:05:38,319 --> 00:05:38,720
He...

118
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:39,240
Chairman Zheng.

119
00:05:41,519 --> 00:05:42,519
We compared them,

120
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,079
and President Su's company's quote

121
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:45,199
and proposal are the best.

122
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:46,519
I've already called her

123
00:05:46,519 --> 00:05:47,319
to come in for a meeting.

124
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,639
Since you've made your choice,

125
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,399
no matter which firm you sign,

126
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,959
follow my terms on payment.

127
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,759
It must be paid in one lump sum.

128
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,000
Understood.

129
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:59,079
Chairman Zheng, rest assured.

130
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:01,319
President Su's company is fully capable.

131
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,199
Let's leave it at that.

132
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:15,879
Chairman Zheng.

133
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:17,680
Hello, Chairman Zheng.

134
00:06:18,279 --> 00:06:19,240
Hello, President Su.

135
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:20,759
You got here fast.

136
00:06:21,399 --> 00:06:22,199
For the contract matters,

137
00:06:22,319 --> 00:06:23,120
you'll work directly with Junjie.

138
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,040
Alright.

139
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,600
He won't look at me.

140
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,639
Is he embarrassed,

141
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,959
or upset about last night?

142
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:48,000
President He, here's your contract.

143
00:06:50,279 --> 00:06:52,279
And Director Qin from Jianrun Supervision

144
00:06:52,279 --> 00:06:53,720
is waiting in the reception room.

145
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:55,800
Got it.

146
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:56,720
Go entertain him first.

147
00:06:56,839 --> 00:06:57,319
Yes, sir.

148
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,199
President Su.

149
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,240
This way, please.

150
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:13,959
Here's the contract you wanted.

151
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:30,680
1.04 billion.

152
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:32,240
Paid in full within ten days.

153
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,360
He Junjie, are you serious?

154
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,439
President Su.

155
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,839
Wanhe Mansion Phase Two

156
00:07:37,839 --> 00:07:38,839
totals 40,000 square meters.

157
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,720
The market price has already exceeded

158
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:41,639
30,000 yuan per square meter.

159
00:07:42,279 --> 00:07:43,279
The current underwriting unit price

160
00:07:43,279 --> 00:07:44,439
is 26,000 yuan.

161
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,360
Your profit margin is huge.

162
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:48,639
If you don't think it's suitable,

163
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:49,560
you can pass.

164
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,360
I still have a client waiting.

165
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:54,279
We've been friends for so many years.

166
00:07:54,759 --> 00:07:56,079
Is there really no room to negotiate?

167
00:07:58,199 --> 00:07:58,839
President Su.

168
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,600
This isn't the first time

169
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,560
you've worked with our company.

170
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:04,000
It's not like you just met me and Yifan.

171
00:08:04,879 --> 00:08:06,079
With this price,

172
00:08:06,879 --> 00:08:07,959
you still don't think it's good enough?

173
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,120
But paying in full within ten days

174
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:12,279
is really too tight.

175
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:14,959
President Su.

176
00:08:15,759 --> 00:08:17,639
If you're not interested in working with us,

177
00:08:18,399 --> 00:08:20,160
then I won't waste your time.

178
00:08:26,879 --> 00:08:29,560
This price is actually decent.

179
00:08:29,879 --> 00:08:31,959
Throw in some gimmicks during sales,

180
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:33,799
stagger the price hikes,

181
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,799
and the profits will be substantial.

182
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,039
President Su.

183
00:08:39,639 --> 00:08:40,399
President Su.

184
00:08:41,759 --> 00:08:42,600
Any other questions?

185
00:08:45,039 --> 00:08:45,840
No.

186
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,720
I'll go back, sign it and send it to you.

187
00:08:48,159 --> 00:08:49,399
But on launch day,

188
00:08:49,799 --> 00:08:50,639
you absolutely must attend.

189
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,039
Sure, no problem.

190
00:08:52,879 --> 00:08:53,440
I'm off.

191
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:54,240
Take care.

192
00:08:58,440 --> 00:09:01,639
We have less than 50% of the funds needed.

193
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:04,399
Loan procedures take time to process.

194
00:09:04,559 --> 00:09:06,799
What about the rest of the money?

195
00:09:08,039 --> 00:09:10,720
We can borrow some from Auntie.

196
00:09:17,679 --> 00:09:18,440
You haven't left yet?

197
00:09:19,159 --> 00:09:19,679
In a bit.

198
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:21,159
How's it going on your end?

199
00:09:21,919 --> 00:09:22,720
Standard procedure.

200
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:24,120
President Su signs and stamps it.

201
00:09:25,799 --> 00:09:26,440
Yifan.

202
00:09:27,159 --> 00:09:28,080
I have an idea.

203
00:09:28,919 --> 00:09:29,759
I need your support.

204
00:09:30,759 --> 00:09:32,240
Since when are you so formal with me?

205
00:09:32,879 --> 00:09:33,360
Go ahead.

206
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:37,159
Your wife works at the bank, right?

207
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,120
The bank audits accounts every month.

208
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:40,840
I want Yang Hui to keep an eye on

209
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,120
Han Lin's personal account.

210
00:09:46,639 --> 00:09:48,320
I'm not sure if bank regulations

211
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:49,879
allow that kind of thing.

212
00:09:50,519 --> 00:09:51,279
I'll go home and ask her.

213
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,960
Why would you think of that?

214
00:09:57,519 --> 00:09:58,440
Once bitten,

215
00:09:58,799 --> 00:09:59,799
twice shy.

216
00:10:00,639 --> 00:10:02,720
I doubt the incident 7 years ago is over.

217
00:10:03,879 --> 00:10:05,480
I keep feeling someone's behind the scenes,

218
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,639
waiting for the chance to take us down.

219
00:10:09,759 --> 00:10:11,840
There's no hatred without reason.

220
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:13,840
Think about all these years,

221
00:10:14,279 --> 00:10:15,399
we haven't offended anyone.

222
00:10:15,759 --> 00:10:17,039
So what's the reason behind it?

223
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:21,720
President He, the client asks how long.

224
00:10:22,159 --> 00:10:23,279
Okay, I'll be right there.

225
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:24,639
I'll get going then.

226
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:32,519
That's impossible.

227
00:10:32,679 --> 00:10:34,240
All our paperwork is in order.

228
00:10:34,799 --> 00:10:35,080
And another thing,

229
00:10:35,679 --> 00:10:37,120
when will your arranged loan come through?

230
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:38,320
President Fang,

231
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:40,200
the loan may be delayed a few days.

232
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:41,360
Don't give me reasons.

233
00:10:41,679 --> 00:10:42,720
I don't want to hear any excuses.

234
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:43,440
I only want results.

235
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:45,080
You have two days to get back to me.

236
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,480
What is going on?

237
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,799
Ever since we got Plot Six,

238
00:10:57,799 --> 00:10:59,039
nothing has gone smoothly.

239
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:03,879
Auntie,

240
00:11:05,879 --> 00:11:06,679
look what I bought!

241
00:11:09,159 --> 00:11:09,840
Buy, buy, buy.

242
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:11,200
All you do is spend money.

243
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:12,200
Don't you want to save anything?

244
00:11:13,919 --> 00:11:15,600
Aww, who upset you this time?

245
00:11:15,759 --> 00:11:16,679
Don't be in a bad mood.

246
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:18,519
I've got good news for you.

247
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:19,440
What good news?

248
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:21,320
I've got nothing but bad news lately.

249
00:11:22,919 --> 00:11:24,240
First, look what I bought you.

250
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:27,960
Your favorite classic style.

251
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,440
It is quite pretty.

252
00:11:33,039 --> 00:11:34,639
Out with it. What's the good news?

253
00:11:36,399 --> 00:11:38,679
I secured the agency for Wanhe Phase Two.

254
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:42,240
Lend me some money first,

255
00:11:42,519 --> 00:11:43,120
just to tide things over.

256
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:44,840
I'll pay you back very soon.

257
00:11:45,679 --> 00:11:46,799
Tell me, how much?

258
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:51,480
The lowest underwriting price,

259
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:52,840
I've already secured it.

260
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:54,759
But I must pay in full within ten days.

261
00:11:55,559 --> 00:11:56,639
Lend me 600 million first.

262
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,240
What?

263
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,000
600 million?
